                        <p>Hopefully something interesting awaits</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item left">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>To be Determined...</h3>
                        <span class="year">The Future</span>
                        <p>Hopefully something interesting awaits</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item right">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>Computer Science Degree</h3>
                        <span class="year">2024 - present</span>
                        <p>Currently enrolled in a bachelors degree of computer science, with a concentration in distributed systems.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>